Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.18,0:00:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.13,0:00:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When watching Kaleido Star,\Nplease keep the room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.84,0:00:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.09,0:00:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm Sora Naegino.\NI came to America all by myself{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.78,0:00:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with aspirations of joining Kaleido Stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.50,0:00:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything is new to me, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.17,0:00:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I'm doing my best in the spirit\Nof "try it rather than think about it."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's nothing I can't do if I try,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and if I can do it without\Ntrying, that'll be super lucky.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.77,0:00:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if I'm gonna do it, I just\Ngotta do it! Gotta! Gotta! That's me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.70,0:00:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well, do you\Nknow anyone who's difficult?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rosetta seems to be just that kind of person.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.35,0:00:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's a talented diabolo performer,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I end up performing with her on stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:00:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But wait, I've never\Nworked with diabolo before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.93,0:01:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh boy, what should I do? What? What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is it that you want to do? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.65,0:01:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time I was asked that {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.50,0:01:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I looked up at the blue sky {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.29,0:01:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The answer is only in my heart {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't easily say the\Nwords that are really important{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I start running towards\Nthe place the light points to{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's so much in my heart\Nthat I want to embrace, I could cry{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:02:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll keep painting my way,\NI promise, take it someday{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Beyond the horizon,\Nwhere the white clouds drift{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The future is lined up and\Nit'll always be there by my side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Jonathan's pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.12,0:02:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how it turned out\Nafter I followed Kalos's request.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that Jonathan seems to like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great, it's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so big.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's ignoring us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ungrateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.61,0:03:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I won't be able to be\Nwith him all the time anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marion, Vince is back from the market.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your meal is here, Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vince, Jonathan says he's tired of waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Amazing Girl Who Doesn't Smile"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Rosetta.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your provisional contract lasts one week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After you finish tonight's performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll do a formal contract including\Nan extension of your time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you understand these arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The French diabolo prodigy\Nperformer is finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a fan of hers, so I couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just passing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We weren't eavesdropping or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not going to buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, come in for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss wants to ask you to\Nbe a guide for the guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.77,0:04:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.48,0:04:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Sora Naegino.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She will take you to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should rest a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.45,0:04:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sora Naegino, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well, I'm your fan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Layla Hamilton?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not in yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your baggage has already\Nbeen delivered to the dormitory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.07,0:04:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Rosetta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for building\Na big pool for Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your room, Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea breeze is nice, so\NI'll keep the windows open, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Kalos only arranged a regular\Nroom for me like the ones you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the youngest winner in\Nthe world diabolo competition,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.82,0:05:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I won for the next four years straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I remember watching you on TV
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you were the youngest\Nto win the competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.78,0:05:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were answering TV interviewers\Nso actively despite being so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I remember it so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.98,0:05:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Traveling around the world from\None circus to another all by herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a French born genius child \Nperformer of diabolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Belgium.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was born in Belgium and studied in France.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to be my guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you don't know\Nanything about me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally come to Kaleido Stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the super diabolo performed\Nby world champion Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to be a world champion yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can get your own diabolo\Nat our gift shop starting at $30.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We want you to like, teach us diabolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My agreement with my agent does not allow me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to display my diabolo\Nperformance except on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please shut the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like, poor little me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That girl is amazing.\N--She's a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's amazing. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I wonder why? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not that fun to watch. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's like a well-oiled diabolo machine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, I'm bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A clown's coming on stage after this, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for an intermission now. Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla, how was my performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were no mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll enjoy your show for the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.33,0:08:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I can be with you longer than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like you're quite confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta, I need to talk to you.\NCan you spare a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the contract extension, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Today is your last performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.05,0:08:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should have picked something\Nmore suited for a younger audience?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for the pay, I will pay you one\Nweek's worth as agreed in the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't need to\Nappear on stage anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, everyone, it's almost time to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I demand a satisfactory explanation\Nfrom you in the dressing room!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going just for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, it's almost our turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta, your diabolo is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I invited you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the audience at Kaleido\NStage did not enjoy your diabolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.83,0:08:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized that when I \Nwatched your show today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:09:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll rearrange the diabolo combinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta, I'm sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't make any mistakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a perfect performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't enjoy my diabolo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because the audience at Kaleido\NStage isn't sophisticated enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are saying that\Nit's the audience's fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.87,0:09:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You believe you're right and\Nyou can stay the way you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.05,0:09:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a world champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world recognizes my diabolo skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage exists to \Nentertain the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the audience was not\Nenjoying your performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't they enjoy my performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage is not an athletic\Nevent to show off your skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will talk to your agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken, when you have time, take\NRosetta and show her around Marine Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.20,0:09:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat me like I'm stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She runs fast too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, you're really not\Ngoing to allow her on stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was not a show.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's only after one show...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.54,0:10:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watching it once was enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She may be able to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind bringing\NRosetta back on stage, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to be with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The contract is for six more days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During that period, you do what\Nyou can to get her back on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that is to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.59,0:10:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:52.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Act two of Cinderella \Nwill be starting shortly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, no! Let's hurry, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.69,0:10:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I've never done diabolo before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.60,0:11:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a crucial time for you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My performance is always perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.42,0:11:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you were little, that was enough\Nfor you to get plenty of attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.19,0:11:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the number of jobs \Nhas decreased recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to change a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.14,0:11:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there for a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm performing flawlessly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.43,0:11:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just tell\Nhim that you can't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.19,0:11:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, why don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I'll still give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.71,0:11:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Miss Sarah! Miss Sarah!\N We have a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, that {\i1}is {\i0}a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she left for home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.77,0:11:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta! Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really! Where did you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Rosetta! Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, Sora, she's right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:11:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does Kalos want me to pair up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think you can do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm planning on trying first,\Nrather than thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, if you start thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you only worry about things,\Nlike, "What if I make a mistake?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it makes for a fun show.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should always expect\Nourselves to perform flawlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better not to do it \Nthan to make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can perform like you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I want them to at least enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.26,0:12:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, maybe it's more about\Ntrying hard than being perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Working hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.27,0:12:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got these for you.\NI thought they could be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Where did you get these?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We stocked too many.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering what to do with all these.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:12:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I didn't mean it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The audience didn't enjoy my show.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Rosetta. Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, maybe I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was nine years old when\Nshe won the world championship,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if I remember correctly,\Nshe started diabolo when she was five.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that age, I just loved Kaleido\NStage and enjoyed watching it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.22,0:13:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without thinking about anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.18,0:13:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She may never have had a chance to\Nenjoy the show as part of the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken, I'm going to give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:13:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ken?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A show that's not perfect,\Nbut still entertaining? What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, do you know the people on that bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been following us the whole way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.10,0:14:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora wants you to see her show.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch! What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a saurel! Saurel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.21,0:14:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing good, Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back, Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.93,0:15:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta! Here, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.50,0:15:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to take a quick look. Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, jump in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.44,0:15:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, you're awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan's better than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Jonathan! Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.07,0:15:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing good, Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! There! I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.43,0:15:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.82,0:15:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:16:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm watching Sora's\Nshow, it makes me nervous,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because I'm worried she's\Ngoing to make a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She does, in fact, make mistakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--but once in a while, she \Ncan be incredibly wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, where are you, Jonathan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.22,0:16:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable, like magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch Sora's performance today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora's performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's completely different from my show.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:17:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta! You came to see the show!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see what our diabolo\Nperformance might look like together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.16,0:17:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll do it perfectly,\Nwhile I try really hard at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that'll be interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to do that, Sora's diabolo\Nneeds to improve a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of thinking, I'll just try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it as if you're going toward the diabolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't actually collide with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The upright Devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It means that she needs\Nto make extreme efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.12,0:17:52.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:52.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good. One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reading Tarot cards by\Nmyself only makes me feel empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.34,0:18:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This... this... this is really tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only one more day left until the time limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to goof off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they've\Nmanaged to make the deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Building a new set in such a hurry was tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think it's an interesting idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say it was their idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They make a good team.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.81,0:18:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, at last, it's time for the\Nfirst diabolo battle in history!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.89,0:18:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this corner, the world diabolo champion,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.41,0:18:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the other corner, with\Nfive days of diabolo experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.27,0:18:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's see the long-awaited\Noutcome of this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.97,0:19:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing good! Go, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta, don't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta made a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:19:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Winner, Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.56,0:20:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo! Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You changed Rosetta, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, I remember back\Nwhen I was nine years old
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and competing in the world championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was smiling behind the interviewers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was saying,\N"It was fun," or "It was interesting."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.25,0:20:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I really felt\Nglad I was doing diabolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I completely forgot how\Nhappy I was during that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time when I loved diabolo so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.59,0:21:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Kaleido Stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and thanks to you, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.31,0:21:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec, Rosetta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.06,0:21:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.21,0:21:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I owe it to you, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to your magic, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're going home after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.43,0:21:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Thank you, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.68,0:21:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday's show was\Nsuccessful because of your talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.19,0:21:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was very captivating.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.03,0:21:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.01,0:21:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I owe it all to Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.59,0:22:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really would have\Nliked to extend the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.87,0:22:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your revenge for\Nwhat happened a week ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.82,0:22:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go home and develop\Nmy own diabolo over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.96,0:22:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, you look like your\Ngirlfriend just broke up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.43,0:22:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's what I feel like.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.14,0:22:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you again, Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.44,0:22:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Merci, {\i0}Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.32,0:22:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you're lonely, what do you do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.00,0:22:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Never say you don't get any of that{\i0}
